author: Ken Thomas, Associated Press
title: Clinton backs potential no-fly zone in Syria
text: Photo: Steven Senne, AP Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Rodham Clinton speaks during a forum on substance abuse, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015, in Boston. Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Rodham Clinton speaks... BOSTON (AP) — Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Rodham Clinton says she would push for a no-fly zone and safe regions in Syria to address the humanitarian crisis that has spilled out in the Middle East.
